key_insights[15]: "IV Rank >70 = sell premium, <30 = buy premium (Barchart/Schwab)","GEX positive = reduces volatility, negative = amplifies volatility",0DTE options now 51% of total S&P 500 options volume (2025),Unusual Whales API provides options flow + dark pool + congressional trading data,Polygon.io (now Massive) covers 1.67M+ options tickers with 7yr history,"Finnhub sentiment API: 30 calls/sec, bullish/bearish %, sector comparison",ApeWisdom API tracks Reddit/4chan stock mentions with 15-min recalculation,SpotGamma provides gamma squeeze candidates + GEX levels,"Databento: OPRA data, Python/Rust/C++ SDKs, $125 free credits for new signups","Alpha Vantage: free tier with 60+ technical indicators + news sentiment API","Captain Solutions: FinTwit sentiment models $20-30/month","FlowAlgo: dark pool + options flow $149/month","Market Chameleon: IV analysis + options screeners $99/month","yfinance: free but delayed/unreliable options chain data","Tradier API: free for brokerage account holders, ORATS Greeks included"
findings[11]: Volatility smile/skew analysis reveals market crash probability expectations,"IV crush after earnings: sell premium strategies (straddles/strangles) most profitable","FOMC 0DTE strategy: credit spreads 1% from market 15-30 min before announcement",Golden/Death Cross (50/200 SMA) as lagging confirmation for options entry,RSI+MACD+Bollinger combined signals increase options entry accuracy,"TA-Lib v0.6.8 (Oct 2025): 150+ indicators, Python 3.9-3.13","pandas-ta: 150+ indicators with numba acceleration",Academic research shows Twitter sentiment improves options strategy by 35.4%,"65% of hedge funds now use ML, AI trading market projected $75.5B by 2034",Trade Ideas Holly AI runs millions of simulated trades daily,"QuantConnect LEAN engine: open-source, supports options backtesting with alt data"
